"marihuana, cannabis medicinal, cannabis recreativa, índica, sativa, híbrida"
msgstr ""
"Cannabis catalog, marijuana varieties, cannabis strains, marijuana guide, "
"medicinal cannabis, recreational cannabis, indica, sativa, hybrid"

